{"tid":1479321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲餐廳 銀龍咖啡茶座","createTime":"2019-08-17T00:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T13:24:28.000Z","uid":203177,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"666b6782b3ad1c16d8782e0a57e1d9763b30a59c","tid":1479321,"uid":203177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T00:39:43.000Z","msg":"影片來源：中新網<br />\n<br />\n【橙訊】銀龍咖啡茶座因老闆、夥計、廚師等都由一人承擔，得名「一人茶餐廳」。6月30日老闆李凱瑚開始參加撐警活動，撐警標語貼在牆上。一些示威人士發現後開始對她騷擾詆毀，餐廳也在美食平台上出現大量負面評價。這家經營了51年的餐廳生意額驟然下降。但李凱瑚卻說：「200%不後悔(撐警)。」<br />\n<br />\n據中新社報道，在香港鯉魚門經營茶餐廳的李凱瑚近日向記者講述自己支援員警以及由此引發的連串不愉快經歷時，情緒略有起伏，但撐警態度依然堅定。「我出來撐的是善良的守護香港的警察，全香港也好，全世界也好，核心價值最重要是和諧，我們要站在自己的良心上做事。」<br />\n<br />\n銀龍咖啡茶座<br />\n油塘鯉魚門海傍道中31號B號鋪<br />\n2348 0711<br />\n<a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/uHVQUZfsFsCt8biw9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaps.app.goo.gl%2FuHVQUZfsFsCt8biw9&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75QRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=e497db61\" target=\"_blank\">https://maps.app.goo.gl/uHVQUZfsFsCt8biw9</a><br />\n大家幫手寫下食評 俾個星讚下佢啲嘢有幾咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529f96e854592f31011d0af951387dace642051e","tid":1479321,"uid":203177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T00:43:11.000Z","msg":"銀龍咖啡茶座<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://maps.app.goo.gl/uHVQUZfsFsCt8biw9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaps.app.goo.gl%2FuHVQUZfsFsCt8biw9&d=u3dPEc69Okhs1BcqxCk75QRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=e497db61\" target=\"_blank\">https://maps.app.goo.gl/uHVQUZfsFsCt8biw9</a><br />\n<br />\n大家幫手寫下食評 俾個星讚下佢啲嘢有幾咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a7eb75